data.description: Great location in Tellico Village, near the Yacht Club and Wellness Center. 1.5 story Cape Cod house with a nice front porch and lots of windows to enjoy views of the lake. 9-foot ceilings with a vaulted ceiling in the 20' x 14' living room. Kitchen boasts granite countertops and breakfast bar, brand new refrigerator, along with a 5-burner gas cooktop. Primary first floor 15' x 14' bedroom has two closets, one walk-in, for his and her wardrobes. Primary bath has an ornate tile walk-in shower and whirlpool tub with separate toilet. Beautiful hardwood floors in entry way, kitchen, sun room, and dining room. The 13' x 12' second bedroom adjoins a full bathroom. The large third bedroom is on the second floor with its own full bathroom. An oversized two car garage with a 220V outlet with plenty of storage and is positioned behind the house. Back patio and private backyard.
